{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0003", "text": "如果 你最好 是最壞藉口 別人未接受", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 5, 4, 9, 2, 4, 2, 2, 9, 2, 0, 2, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyu4", "gwo2", "nei5", "zeoi3", "hou2", "si6", "zeoi3", "waai6", "zik6", "hau2", "bit6", "jan4", "mei6", "zip3", "sau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "如果", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最壞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藉口", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "別人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "接受", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0004", "text": "就含淚笑笑 讓旁人收口", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 0, 2, 4, 4, 2, 0, 0, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zau6", "ham4", "leoi6", "siu3", "siu3", "joeng6", "pong4", "jan4", "sau1", "hau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "就", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "含淚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "笑笑", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "旁人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "收口", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0005", "text": "頑強活到今時的我 壞的好的 見太多", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 0, 3, 5, 2, 3, 9, 3, 4, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "koeng4", "wut6", "dou3", "gam1", "si4", "dik1", "ngo5", "waai6", "dik1", "hou2", "dik1", "gin3", "taai3", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "頑強", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "活到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今時", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "壞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "見太多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0006", "text": "誰人在暗中扶起我 (狂潮越過低潮衝過", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 0, 9, 5, 0, 2, 4, 3, 0, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["seoi4", "jan4", "zoi6", "am3", "zung1", "fu4", "hei2", "ngo5", "ciu4", "jyut6", "gwo3", "dai1", "ciu4", "cung1", "gwo3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "暗中", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "扶起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "(", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "狂潮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "低潮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "衝", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "過", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0007", "text": "還怎會不清楚 才明白我要什麼)", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 9, 3, 3, 9, 0, 0, 2, 5, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "zam2", "bat1", "cing1", "co2", "coi4", "ming4", "baak6", "ngo5", "jiu3", "sam6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怎會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "清楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "明白", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "什麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": ")", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0008", "text": "(來)做我女人好 麼 讓我愛惜好 麼", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 5, 5, 0, 9, 3, 2, 5, 4, 3, 9, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zou6", "ngo5", "neoi5", "jan4", "hou2", "mo1", "joeng6", "ngo5", "oi3", "sik1", "hou2", "mo1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "(", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": ")", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "女人", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛惜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "麼", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0009", "text": "從前負擔許 多 今天 交給 我", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 3, 9, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["cung4", "cin4", "fu6", "daam1", "heoi2", "do1", "gam1", "tin1", "gaau1", "kap1", "ngo5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "從前", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "負擔", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "許", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "今天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "交給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0010", "text": "潮流有許多 個 沒有變的不 多", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 5, 9, 3, 4, 2, 5, 4, 3, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ciu4", "lau4", "jau5", "heoi2", "do1", "go3", "mut6", "jau5", "bin3", "dik1", "bat1", "do1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "潮流", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "許多", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "變", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "多", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "我女人", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_2085", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_MjA4NQ_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
